<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>طَلْح <span class="c4">[جمع]</span>: جج طلوح،<span class="c5"> مف طلحة:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
